<p>Chloe said the trolls have got 'inside my head' after being inundated with cruel taunts calling her 'fat and ugly every day'. </p>

<p>The reality star's girly getaway comes after she ignored speculation she had faked a trip to Ibiza and had instead secretly joined her ex boyfriend Sam Gowland, 25, in Dubai.</p>

<p>It had recently been reported that the star had back together with her co-star ex - despite being in the throes of filming Celebs Go Dating. </p>

